  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <p>
      Welcome to Furniture Hub — your go-to destination for premium, elegant, and modern furniture collections.
      Our mission is to enhance your living spaces with designs that combine comfort, simplicity, and luxury.
    </p>
    <p>
      From cozy beds to elegant dining sets, classy living room decor to functional study tables — we've got it all.
      Each product is curated to transform your house into a warm, inviting, and beautiful home.
    </p>
    <p>
      We believe every home deserves to be both beautiful and practical. Our collections are hand-picked to bring you 
      furniture crafted from the finest materials, featuring thoughtful designs and lasting quality.
    </p>
    <p>
